# vDSP_biquadm_CopyStateD

**Function**

Copies the filter state from one double-precision multichannel biquadratic IIR filter object to another.

## Declaration

```swift
extern void vDSP_biquadm_CopyStateD(vDSP_biquadm_SetupD __dest, const struct vDSP_biquadm_SetupStructD * __src);
```

## Discussion

This function is the same as [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/kernel/1579980-vdsp_biquadm_copystate], except for the types of the `src` and `dest` objects.

## Copying the filter state of a multichannel biquadratic filter

- **vDSP_biquadm_CopyState**: Copies the filter state from one single-precision multichannel biquadratic IIR filter object to another.
